SD=Customer Portfolio
CR= Customer Segment Analysis
BQs=PerformanceAnalysis      
Maintain a portfolio of view of the customer base with key customer data and consolidated activity details to support profitability and performance analysis across many possible customer segment dimensions
Business development review customer segment performance in order to target customer relationship management priorities
Maintain a portfolio of analytical views of the customer base to support customer segment profitability and performance analysis
CR - Customer Segment Analysis				BQ 1 - Performance Analysis					
Ev	Up	Rq	Re	Ev	Up	Ec	Ex	Rq	Re
EvCR Evaluate customer segment performance (trigger the analysis)
UpCR Update settings or content for customer segment analysis activity
RqCR Request manual intervention in the customer segment analysis activity (e.g. ad-hoc request)
ReCR Retrieve details about customer segment analysis activity
EvBQ Evaluate customer segment performance using a specific type of analysis
UpBQ Update details of a specific customer segment performance analysis
EcBQ Accept, reject, verify, etc. customer segment analysis
ExBQ Execute an automated action against on-going analysis (e.g. refresh source production data)
RqBQ Request manual intervention to on-going analysis (e.g. amend analysis scope/approach)
ReBQ Retrieve details about a specific customer segment performance analysis